    <item>
      <title>If You’re So Smart, Why Aren’t You Happy?</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/if-youre-so-smart-why-arent-you-happy/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2020 15:02:38 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/if-youre-so-smart-why-arent-you-happy/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/if-youre-so-smart-why-arent-you-happy.zh/&#34;&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://nav.al/smart&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://nav.al/smart&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://nav.al/smart&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;div&#xA;  class=&#34;link-card group relative my-3 w-full overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--lc-border,rgba(15,23,42,0.12))] bg-[var(--lc-bg,var(--card-bg,var(--surface,#ffffff))))] transition-shadow duration-150 hover:shadow-[var(--lc-shadow-hover,0_14px_30px_-18px_rgba(15,23,42,0.35))]&#34;&#xA;  data-url=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;a&#xA;    class=&#34;link-card__fallback block px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--lc-url,var(--link-color,#0e6a85))] underline-offset-4 hover:underline&#34;&#xA;    href=&#34;https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#34;&#xA;    target=&#34;_blank&#34;&#xA;    rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;    https://x.com/naval/status/1002103360646823936&#xA;  &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;h1 id=&#34;if-youre-so-smart-why-arent-you-happy&#34;&gt;If You&amp;rsquo;re So Smart, Why Aren&amp;rsquo;t You Happy?&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Feb 12 2020&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can increase your happiness without losing your drive&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&amp;ldquo;Happiness is for stupid people.&amp;rdquo; That&amp;rsquo;s a common complaint I hear from smart overachievers. They think only dumb or lazy people can be happy. Entrepreneurs will say, &amp;ldquo;I don&amp;rsquo;t want to be happy because I want to be successful.&amp;rdquo; They worry that if they get too happy they&amp;rsquo;ll lose their desire and won&amp;rsquo;t work hard anymore.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
